import React from 'react' import {Container, Card, Row, Col, Button} from 'react-bootstrap' import {LinkContainer} from 'react-router-bootstrap' const LoggedInProfile = ({firstName, lastName, email, gradYear, meetingsAttended, yearsInClub, leadershipPosition}) => { return (
Name: {firstName} {lastName} Email: {email} Email: {email} Graduating in {gradYear}!
Total meetings attended: {meetingsAttended}
Years in club: {yearsInClub}
{leadershipPosition ? "Leadership position: " + leadershipPosition : ""}
) } export default LoggedInProfile
